---
title: Moroccan Spiced Cod Parcel with Fragrant Couscous and Orange Dressing
description: It’s no secret that our chef Vix prides herself on her Moroccan inspired recipes. Chef André thought he would give her a bit of a run
for her money and team a sweet and delicately flavoured Moroccan couscous with spicy cod. Even Vix thinks this one is a winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-spiced-cod-parcel-wk40-0a03e03a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/moroccan-spiced-cod-parcel-wk40-5b093f04.pdf
time required: 25 minutes
servings: 2
